title: Michael Jackson - This Is It OST - Audiophile Remastered
description:
Michael Jackson Rehearsals - from "This is it" movie.

Remastered and mixed by me. No compressors or limiters used. Just pure, crystal sounding audio without any clipping. I used the DTS track from original Blu-Ray.
